id He % kind of elements
natom  864 % number of atoms
mass 4.0026 % unit in g/mol

geo_dir geo1.in % routes of initial configurations, default in same work directory.
read_vel 1 % 1: read initial velocity from initial configurations; 2: produce random initial velocity
temp 300 % unit in K
step 1    % unit in ps
nstep 1 % MD simulation steps

rcut 8.5 % rcut for Leonard-Jones potential in \AA 
neighbor_r 2 % extra distance for neighbor list in \AA
neighbor_n 300 % maximum number of neighboring atoms

epsilon 0.01032 % LJ potential parameters
sigma 3.405 